weblog ping for Mephisto
==================================================

Upon posting an article, a ping will be sent


Install
==========
   ruby script/install svn://hasno.info/mephisto/plugins/mephisto_post_ping


Usage
==========
   Post an article. The plugin defaults to pinging ping-o-matic (http://pingomatic.com).
   If you would like to change what sites the plugin pings, do the following:

ArticlePingObserver::SERVICES = [ "http://my.api.site", "http://another.api.site" ]

   you can also append to the services list

ArticlePingObserver::SERVICES << "http://my.ping.site"



